# OpenAI API Endpoints

This library provides access to the following OpenAI API endpoints:

## Chat Completions

- Module: [OpenAI.V1.Chat.Completions](mdc:src/OpenAI/V1/Chat/Completions.hs)
- Method: `createChatCompletion`
- Creates a completion for a chat conversation

## Models

- Module: [OpenAI.V1.Models](mdc:src/OpenAI/V1/Models.hs)
- Methods: `listModels`, `retrieveModel`, `deleteModel`
- Lists, retrieves, and deletes models

## Images

- Module: [OpenAI.V1.Images](mdc:src/OpenAI/V1/Images.hs)
- Methods: `createImage`, `createImageEdit`, `createImageVariation`
- Generates, edits, and creates variations of images

## Embeddings

- Module: [OpenAI.V1.Embeddings](mdc:src/OpenAI/V1/Embeddings.hs)
- Method: `createEmbeddings`
- Creates embeddings for input text

## Files

- Module: [OpenAI.V1.Files](mdc:src/OpenAI/V1/Files.hs)
- Methods: `uploadFile`, `listFiles`, `retrieveFile`, `deleteFile`, `retrieveFileContent`
- Manages files used for fine-tuning and other purposes

## Audio

- Module: [OpenAI.V1.Audio](mdc:src/OpenAI/V1/Audio.hs)
- Methods: `createSpeech`, `createTranscription`, `createTranslation`
- Handles text-to-speech, transcription, and translation

## Fine-tuning

- Module: [OpenAI.V1.FineTuning.Jobs](mdc:src/OpenAI/V1/FineTuning/Jobs.hs)
- Methods: `createFineTuningJob`, `listFineTuningJobs`, etc.
- Manages fine-tuning jobs

## Assistants, Threads, and Runs

- Modules: `OpenAI.V1.Assistants`, `OpenAI.V1.Threads`, `OpenAI.V1.Threads.Runs`
- Methods: Various CRUD operations for assistants, threads, and runs
- Implements the assistants API for complex multi-turn conversations

Additional endpoints are available for moderations, vector stores, and other OpenAI services. Refer to the `Methods` record in [src/OpenAI/V1.hs](mdc:src/OpenAI/V1.hs) for a complete list.
